cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.SY

This paper deals with improving the spectral efficiency of wireless systems through cognitive radio, which is a subfield of networked systems and computer communication (cs.NI). The proposed algorithm involves reinforcement learning (cs.AI) and Bayesian approaches (cs.LG) to optimize channel selection and sensing duration. The paper also discusses interference management (cs.IT) and achieving higher throughput (cs.SY).
